  "keyFeatures": [
    "Multiboot2-compliant x86_64 kernel loaded at 1 MB",
    "32-bit RGB linear framebuffer with double-buffering",
    "Custom SilverFS filesystem on ATA/PIO block storage",
    "RTL8139 Ethernet driver with ARP, IPv4, and ICMP (ping) support",
    "Windowed graphical desktop environment with taskbar, login screen, and Z-ordering window manager",
    "Built-in terminal application with shell commands (ls, cat, mkdir, ping, free, date)",
    "PS/2 keyboard and mouse drivers with interrupt-driven input",
    "Physical memory manager (bitmap-based) and kernel heap allocator",
    "GDT, IDT, PIC, and TSS hardware initialization",
    "Host-side mkfs_svd tool for creating SilverFS virtual disk images",
    "QEMU-runnable ISO image with GRUB2 Multiboot2 bootloader",
    "Serial port debug output on COM1"
  ],
